data.description: Energy efficient, Rastra construction w stucco exterior. Inside repurposed  barn board planks line the kitchen/dining walls as well as the living room ceilings. Interior door trim and window casings are all hand hewn wood giving the home a warm/rustic feel and offer low maintenance. An AZ room invites casual dining or a game room and leads to the laundry area off to one end.  Massive peeled posts support the south facing rear patio roof.  The free standing 'bunkhouse' presents many possibilities, with  2 BRs and one bath w/sitting area.  A 24 by 24 detached garage has storage at one end and a full floored loft w/a deck..a true blank canvas. Fenced and cross fenced w/a two stall horse shelter  ready for the critters..even has home for the chickens! Mature trees and shrubs provide shad Home is heated and cooled w/gas pack.  Well is on the property within a fenced area.  Perimeter fencing is primarily barbed wire. Bunkhouse has window AC unit. This property is in an estate, PR has not lived there, so limited SPDS..and is offered as-is.  No warranties on appliances.
